original_raw:
example (h : ¬ (P ∧ Q)) : ¬ P ∨ ¬ Q  := by
  have hmm : P → ¬ Q := by
    intro p opp
    have duh : P ∧ Q := by
      constructor
      exact p
      exact opp
    exact h duh
  by_cases duh:P
  right
  exact hmm duh
  left
  exact duh
new_raw_BASIC:
example (h : ¬ (P ∧ Q)) : ¬ P ∨ ¬ Q := by
  byCases duh : P
  case pos
    right
    exact hmm duh
  case neg
    left
    exact duh
